data.description:
!!!!WOW!!!! This is the house with all the updates. Are you ready to save money on your Electric Bill??? 
''New Solar Panels'' Installed at no cost to the buyer, fully paid by the seller.
New Roof, New Air Conditioner, New Water Heater, New Heating System, All New Electrical Panels inside and out. New Alkaline Water Filter System installed. The house has been updated with all new Spanish Marble Flooring throughout. All New Windows were installed just 10 years ago. The Basement has a large living space with an additional 2 rooms that could be used as bedrooms and a Large eat-in Kitchen, also a new bathroom was added to the basement 5 months ago. MSD installed a water sewer lock in front yard to prevent flooding. The main bathroom on the first floor has been recently updated with a new jetted tub. This one is a must see, won't last long.
